review_text: This course is amazing, I highly recommend it!  Great video quality, with very smart host teaching the course. Great job guys!

As always, Phil Ebiner is providing outstanding course contents and although I am not a photographer, I can benefit from this great and informative course in many ways. 
What I'd like to point out from a German perspective on how to start a business is that here business consultants are very expensive and charge something up to 800 euros a day. To become an official freelancer and became familiar with our federal laws, I read books on business founding and hired a tax consultant to deal with the authorities.
